    <para styleclass="Normal">When an Alarm has occurred, the Alarm details are displayed on the Alarm Detail Screen.</para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal">To navigate to Alarm Detail Screen, press <text style="font-weight:bold;">[MENU]</text> <text styleclass style="font-family:Symbol; font-size:11pt; color:#000000;">®</text> press Makino icon <text styleclass style="font-family:Symbol; font-size:11pt; color:#000000;">®</text> Main Menu Screen is displayed <text styleclass style="font-family:Symbol; font-size:11pt; color:#000000;">®</text> press Alarm Detail Screen icon <text styleclass style="font-family:Symbol; font-size:11pt; color:#000000;">®</text> Alarm Detail Screen is displayed.</para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"></para>
